ed.  Some of the reports generated are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Follow-up Actions Report</li>\r\n<li>Travel Efficiency Report</li>\r\n<li>Travel Expenses Report</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>On stabilization, workflow for proactive action by the respective employee is planned to be built on top of this application.</p>\r\n<img class="mobile-view" src="images/hawkilogo.png" alt="" width="40%" /></td>\r\n<td class="desktop-view"><center><img src="images/hawkilogo.png" alt="" width="40%" /></center></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<hr />\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="60%">\r\n<p><strong>GIVEBLOODINDIA</strong><br /> Developed a web application for Registration of Donors, Request for Blood and Search of Donors.  Interfacing, Report generation and Messaging are handled. <br /><a href="http://givebloodindia.org/" target="_blank">http://givebloodindia.org</a></p>\r\n<img class="mobile-view" src="images/givebloodindialogo.png" alt="" width="80%" /></td>\r\n<td class="desktop-view"><center><img src="images/givebloodindialogo.png" alt="" width="80%" /></center></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Learning Management</strong><br /> Currently we are developing a MOOC (Massively Organized Online Courses) in health-care Industry for one of our clients.  This MOOC is targeted for UK market for developing specialized skill sets in health care.  This application handles the entire life cycle of the Learning Management including user registration, payment receipt, scheduling and organizing the courses.  The application is under User Acceptance Testing and is expected to go live in end of 2015 or early 2016.</p>', '', 1, 14, '2015-09-25 11:31:50', 40, '', '2016-03-17 15:26:12', 40, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-09-25 11:31:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext"