INSERT INTO `sdjqk_ucm_history` VALUES (222, 6, 1, '', '2015-10-01 07:51:12', 40, 3810, 'dd3715e7950598e26f69a79b68f67a0a01e745a8', '{"id":6,"asset_id":"73","title":"Custom Applications","alias":"custom-applications","introtext":"<p>We believe that each business house is unique and some of them may not be able to find a generic product catering to their unique processes.\\u00a0 Neither any off-the-shelve product exists for them till date. We are very passionate to take up these challenging tasks.\\u00a0 We will provide an innovative and flexible design and deliver the custom solutions in short-time frame without compromising quality.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>GADDIEL<\\/strong> founders are professionals having rich experience in solution definition, prototyping, development, testing and deployment of home-grown custom applications.\\u00a0 Our customers can be assured of an on-time and high quality delivery of their applications with excellent ROI.<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Significant reduction of risk<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Short learning curve and incremental deliverable (Agile\\/Waterfall)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Strong alignment with business &amp; the client''s business case<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Ongoing post-implementation support service<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>Our Services and Solutions are generally a mix of Web Application for the maintenance of the system and Mobile App for field level real time information processing.\\u00a0 We provide cost effective solutions by developing the solutions on open source systems and using cloud-based infrastructure.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Application Enhancement<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Enhancement of an application needs rather special skills like understanding the current application; finding the gaps and developing and deploying solutions that can integrate with the current application and fill the gap.\\u00a0 Gaddiel team has a rich and long experience in such developments including customization''s and enhancements of Oracle Applications a